data.description: Nestled on the northwest side of vibrant San Antonio, this beautiful 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home boasts a stately brick facade and stunning curb appeal. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a bright and spacious interior that offers an open floor plan concept, making it perfect for easy entertaining and everyday living. The fabulous kitchen is a chef's dream, with ample countertop prep space and cabinetry, ideal for creating delicious meals. A charming breakfast nook completes the heart of the home. Upstairs, a versatile loft area awaits, perfect for a second living area, office space, or however you envision it. The primary bedroom is a true retreat, featuring a luxurious en-suite bath. All bedrooms in this home are cozy and provide ample space for rest and relaxation. Outside, the large backyard offers covered areas for outdoor dining and relaxation, extended via beautiful brickwork. Conveniently located on the northwest side of San Antonio, this home provides easy access to all the amenities the city has to offer. It's the ideal place to call home, combining comfort, style, and functionality. Schedule a showing today and experience it for yourself!
